author: By JOHN HANNA Associated Press
title: Kansas stay-at-home rule allows religious worship, gun sales
description: TOPEKA, Kan. (AP) — All 2.9 million Kansas residents were under a stay-at-home order Monday imposed by Democratic Gov. Laura Kelly as the numbers of confirmed coronavirus cases and COVID-19-related deaths continue to grow.
